# Agent Portal Environment Configuration
# ========================================
# Set your preferred API provider. The portal supports:
#   - GitHub Copilot API (requires GitHub token with copilot scope)
#   - OpenAI API
#   - Any OpenAI-compatible endpoint

# --- Option 1: GitHub Copilot API ---
# AGENT_API_BASE=https://api.githubcopilot.com
# AGENT_API_KEY=your-github-token
# AGENT_MODEL=gpt-4o

# --- Option 2: OpenAI API ---
# AGENT_API_BASE=https://api.openai.com/v1
# AGENT_API_KEY=sk-...
# AGENT_MODEL=gpt-4o

# --- Option 3: Any OpenAI-compatible endpoint ---
# AGENT_API_BASE=http://localhost:11434/v1
# AGENT_API_KEY=ollama
# AGENT_MODEL=llama3

